---
import Paper from "../layouts/Paper.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, "");
---
<Paper title="Live Demo · Real API · AI-Driven Payment Scheme Routing">
  <main>
    <header class="paper-col pt-16 md:pt-20 pb-6">
      <a href={`${baseUrl}/`} class="text-muted font-sans text-sm hover:text-accent">&larr; Back to research paper</a>
      <p class="section-num mt-4">Live demo &middot; calls the real deployed Lambda</p>
      <h1 class="mb-4">Try the Routing Agent Live</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-ink/80 mb-2">
        This page posts your transaction to the real <code class="text-[0.95em]">POST /route</code> endpoint
        on AWS API Gateway. The Lambda invokes either Bedrock or the direct Anthropic API,
        runs the full ReAct loop against live DynamoDB tables and the ONNX interchange model,
        and returns a structured routing decision.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="paper-col pb-6">
      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-md p-4 text-sm text-amber-900 mb-6">
        <strong class="font-sans">Heads up &mdash; cold-start latency.</strong>
        A typical run takes <strong>25&ndash;40 seconds</strong> (Bedrock/Anthropic + DynamoDB + ONNX + multiple tool turns).
        API Gateway has a hard <strong>29-second timeout</strong>, so the first call after the
        Lambda goes cold will likely time out at the gateway even though the Lambda completes.
        Retry the same scenario &mdash; warm calls finish in 25&ndash;32 seconds.
      </div>

      <div class="bg-rule/30 border border-rule rounded-md p-4 text-sm text-ink/80 mb-6">
        <strong class="font-sans text-accent">Bedrock vs Anthropic.</strong>
        Bedrock access on this AWS account is still being resolved with AWS Support &mdash; you'll see a
        <code>ThrottlingException</code> if you pick Bedrock. The Anthropic-API path is fully working
        today and produces identical routing decisions (same ReAct loop, same tools, same DynamoDB
        and ONNX backing services).
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="wide-col pb-12">
      <div class="max-w-paper mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

        <!-- LEFT: form -->
        <div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-rule rounded-md p-5 mb-4">
            <label for="scenario-select" class="block text-xs font-sans uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-2">
              Preset scenario
            </label>
            <select id="scenario-select" class="w-full bg-paper border border-rule rounded px-3 py-2 font-serif text-base"></select>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-4 text-sm font-sans">
              <label>
                <span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-1">BIN</span>
                <input id="bin" type="text" class="w-full bg-paper border border-rule rounded px-3 py-2 font-mono" />
              </label>
              <label>
                <span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-1">Last 4</span>
                <input id="last4" type="text" maxlength="4" class="w-full bg-paper border border-rule rounded px-3 py-2 font-mono" />
              </label>
              <label>
                <span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-1">Card type</span>
                <select id="card_type" class="w-full bg-paper border border-rule rounded px-3 py-2">
                  <option>CREDIT</option>
                  <option>DEBIT</option>
                  <option>PREPAID</option>
                </select>
              </label>
              <label>
                <span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-1">Amount</span>
                <input id="amount" type="number" step="0.01" class="w-full bg-paper border border-rule rounded px-3 py-2 font-mono" />
              </label>
              <label>
                <span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-1">Currency</span>
                <input id="currency" type="text" maxlength="3" class="w-full bg-paper border border-rule rounded px-3 py-2 font-mono" />
              </label>
              <label>
                <span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-1">MCC</span>
                <input id="mcc" type="text" maxlength="4" class="w-full bg-paper border border-rule rounded px-3 py-2 font-mono" />
              </label>
              <label>
                <span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-1">Merchant country</span>
                <input id="merchant_country" type="text" maxlength="2" class="w-full bg-paper border border-rule rounded px-3 py-2 font-mono" />
              </label>
              <label>
                <span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-1">Card country</span>
                <input id="card_country" type="text" maxlength="2" class="w-full bg-paper border border-rule rounded px-3 py-2 font-mono" />
              </label>
            </div>

            <label class="block mt-4">
              <span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-1 font-sans">Transaction ID</span>
              <input id="transaction_id" type="text" class="w-full bg-paper border border-rule rounded px-3 py-2 font-mono text-sm" />
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-rule rounded-md p-5 mb-4">
            <div class="text-xs font-sans uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-3">LLM provider</div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm font-sans">
              <label class="border border-rule rounded p-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-rule/30 has-[:checked]:border-accent has-[:checked]:bg-accent/5">
                <input type="radio" name="provider" value="anthropic" checked class="mr-2" />
                <span class="font-semibold text-ink">Anthropic API</span>
                <div class="text-xs text-muted mt-1">claude-sonnet-4-5 · working today</div>
              </label>
              <label class="border border-rule rounded p-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-rule/30 has-[:checked]:border-accent has-[:checked]:bg-accent/5">
                <input type="radio" name="provider" value="bedrock" class="mr-2" />
                <span class="font-semibold text-ink">AWS Bedrock</span>
                <div class="text-xs text-muted mt-1">us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6 · access pending</div>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>

          <button
            id="submit-btn"
            class="w-full bg-accent text-paper font-sans font-medium px-4 py-3 rounded hover:bg-accent/90 transition"
          >
            Route transaction &rarr;
          </button>

          <div class="mt-4 flex items-center justify-between text-sm font-sans">
            <span id="status-badge" class="pill pill-muted">Idle</span>
            <a href={`${baseUrl}/#demo`} class="text-muted hover:text-accent">View pre-recorded version &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT: response -->
        <div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-rule rounded-md p-5">
            <div class="text-xs font-sans uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-3">Routing decision</div>
            <div id="decision-card" class="text-muted italic">
              No request yet. Pick a scenario and press <em>Route transaction</em>.
            </div>

            <div id="raw-section" class="hidden mt-6">
              <details>
                <summary class="text-xs font-sans uppercase tracking-widest text-muted cursor-pointer">
                  Raw response JSON
                </summary>
                <pre id="raw-json" class="font-mono text-[12px] bg-term text-termfg rounded mt-3 p-4 overflow-auto max-h-96 whitespace-pre-wrap"></pre>
              </details>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-muted font-sans leading-relaxed">
            POST <code class="text-[11px]">https://arza8e31vj.execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/prod/route</code>
            <br/>
            CORS is enabled on the API; calls go directly from your browser.
            Lambda function: <code>payment-routing-engine</code> in <code>us-east-1</code>.
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <script>
      import "../scripts/live-demo.ts";
    </script>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Paper>
